WEBVTT

1
00:06:41.650 --> 00:06:42.370 
据我们所知
To our knowledge,

2
00:06:42.370 --> 00:06:44.810 
附近没有居民表现出类似的特征
no other nearby residents have exhibited similar traits.

3
00:06:44.820 --> 00:06:46.570 
那我们是怎么知道他的
So how did we find out about him?

4
00:06:46.570 --> 00:06:48.750 
有线人看见他在街头表演中
Informant saw him lighting torches in a street show...

5
00:06:49.340 --> 00:06:50.770 
用小手指点燃火把
with his pinkie.

6
00:06:50.900 --> 00:06:52.360 
由此引来了神盾局的关注
Brought it to S.H.I.E.L.D.'s attention.

7
00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:54.580 
我们叫他不能随便运用此能力
We told him to keep his abilities under wraps.

8
00:06:54.580 --> 00:06:56.360 
从那时起  他就列入目录上了
He's been on the index ever since.

9
00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:57.240 
什么目录
The index?

10
00:06:57.240 --> 00:06:58.910 
是神盾局保存超能力者与
It's a list S.H.I.E.L.D. keeps of people

11
00:06:58.910 --> 00:06:59.720 
富含能量物体的名单
and objects with powers.

12
00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:02.400 
等等  名单上有多少人啊
Wait. What? How many are there?

13
00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:03.540 
你是说更多的人有...
Are you saying there are more people --

14
00:07:03.540 --> 00:07:04.330 
没有很多
Not many.

15
00:07:04.330 --> 00:07:05.560 
都足够列个名单出来了....
Well, enough to keep a list.

16
00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:07.730 
一份很短的名单  是打算要保护他们
A short list, meant to protect them.

17
00:07:07.740 --> 00:07:10.430 
尽管某些少见的情况下神盾局会采取行动
Though, in rare cases, S.H.I.E.L.D. has had to take action.

18
00:07:10.470 --> 00:07:13.650 
采取行动对付物体还是人
Action against objects or people?

